  <brief_title>Gold Against Pains From Osteoarthrosis in the Knee</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Effects From Implants of Gold Around the Arthrotic Knee Joint. A Randomized, Double Blind, Placebo Controlled Investigation.</official_title>
