  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Gold implantation around arthritic joints is a very popular treatment - but the effect has
      never been controlled.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Randomization between

        1. Gold (4 x 3 berlocks, injected under local anesthesia) and

        2. Sham operation - only local anesthesia Functional and pain measures reported through the
           next 6 months.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
